data.description: Welcome to this exquisite and recently enhanced modern residence situated on a sprawling .78-acre lot at the cul-de-sac within the gated community of English Creek by Southern Homes. This residence offers a total of 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, providing ample space for family and guests. With upgraded luxury vinyl plank flooring gracing the main living areas, this home seamlessly blends style and functionality. The kitchen boasts dark gray wood crowned cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances, creating a sleek culinary space. Additionally, bar stools may be added to the kitchen island, providing a casual and social space for family and guests. The inviting living room is a focal point of the home, featuring sliding glass doors that open up to the lanai, allowing for a seamless indoor-outdoor transition. Ample windows flood the space with natural light, creating a bright and airy atmosphere, while designed for entertaining and hosting, with a decorative wall and entertainment center with a TV that can be set at any light, creating the perfect ambiance. The primary bedroom suite is a true retreat, featuring a double tray ceiling, two separate walk-in closets, and an ensuite bathroom that includes a step-in tiled glass door shower, a garden tub with jets, and two separate vanities. The guest suite includes its own walk-in closet, enhancing privacy and comfort. The outdoor oasis is equally impressive, featuring a brand new saltwater heated pool and spa with a pavered lanai, all installed within the last few months. Enjoy the inviting poolside atmosphere, complete with beautiful accent lighting, and control the settings conveniently through WiFi on your phone. The oversized corner lot, privacy fence, and large screened-in lanai further contribute to the allure of this home. Practical features, such as boat and RV parking in the driveway or behind fencing, cater to an active lifestyle. The property's location is a commuter's dream, just minutes away from I4, and conveniently close to Publix. This residence offers not only a modern and stylish living space but also the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and luxury within a secure and gated community, now enhanced by the recent addition of a stunning pool and spa. All appliances and the outdoor television are included, as well as the bar in the 5th bedroom/office are negotiable. Schedule your tour today and feel the welcome of home!
